CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1952, pg. 20 reads: "At Church Council Meeting - The Rev. O.M. Walton, executive secretary of the Council of Churches; Harbaugh Miller, president of the council; Dr. Clarence A. Burrell, vice president of the group; Mrs. Ruth Graham, Dr. Ainsley C. Moore, also a vice president, and Billy Graham are shone at the ninth annual meeting of Council of Churches at East Liberty Presbyterian Church Monday night. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Rev. O.M. Walton, Harbaugh Miller, Dr. Clarence A. Burrell, Ruth Graham, Dr. Ainsley C. Moore, and Billy Graham, posed in East Liberty Presbyterian Church for annual Council of Churches meeting
